      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of unrivaled caliber, maintained to the most exacting standards. This specimen exhibits a flawless aesthetic and mechanical profile, representative of its showroom-original condition. Every surface, from the meticulously preserved upholstery to the lustrous exterior finish, confirms its status as a premier acquisition for the discerning motorist. We invite you to experience a standard of automotive excellence that transcends the ordinary.",
