    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't find another one like this. It\u2019s been absolutely babied and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! Not a scratch on it, and it drives like a total dream. I've taken such good care of it, and I'm honestly a bit sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Come see it for yourself!",
