    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example that defines 'showroom condition.' This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, retaining its deep, mirror-like factory finish with zero stone chips or imperfections. The interior remains indistinguishable from new, featuring supple leather that still carries the original factory aroma and seat bolsters with absolutely no signs of entry wear. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule by certified technicians, documented in a comprehensive binder included with the sale. Mechanically, it operates with the precision of a car just driven off the lot\u2014silent, powerful, and incredibly tight. From the pristine undercarriage to the untouched spare tire and original tool kit, this is a collector-grade specimen for the most discerning buyer who demands perfection.",
