      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in impeccable mechanical order. This specimen features the legendary S54 inline-six, with documented rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul to ensure optimal variable valve timing. The chassis has been structurally reinforced at the rear subframe mounting points, maintaining factory-spec torsional rigidity. Driving dynamics are sharpened by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential with zero lash. The suspension remains true to its original geometry, utilizing fresh bushings and dampers for that signature analog feedback. This is a turnkey, high-revving masterpiece with no deferred maintenance and a pristine aesthetic to match its mechanical excellence.",
